snippet.title: Minecraft x SpongeBob DLC – Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Join SpongeBob and the rest of your undersea faves in this new DLC! Explore Bikini Bottom’s iconic locations as you complete tasks for Mr. Krabs, Patrick, Squidward, and more. Don’t forget to pick up your free Character Creator item in the dressing room!* More info: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/marketplace/pdp?id=c1c33c20-774d-467e-ac3d-b14b1bccb1a8

*Requires the latest version of Minecraft: Bedrock Edition (sold separately).  Limit 1 free item per person/account.  Free item available from 7/26/22 until 9/27/22.
